ce of an effective temperature. The formal relation between critical\noscillators and equilibrium critical points suggests that long-range phase\norder exists in critical oscillators above two dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2009 13:24:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Feb 2009 20:56:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Feb 2009 21:01:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-09-22"}
